BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (WHY FAMILY MEETINGS WORK) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Regular family meetings teach kids: democracy, problem-solving,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (communication, and that their voice matters.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (- Reduces daily nagging \(decisions made together stick\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (- Kids feel heard and respected) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.0 Td (- Problems get solved before they explode) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.0 Td (- Builds teamwork and family identity) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.0 Td (- Teaches real-world meeting and negotiation skills) Tj ET
endstream
