stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (FAMILY MEETING GROUND RULES) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Post these where everyone can see:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (  1. Everyone gets a turn to talk) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (  2. Listen without interrupting) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (  3. No blaming or name-calling) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.0 Td (  4. Focus on solutions, not problems) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.0 Td (  5. Decisions need agreement \(not just parent vote\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.0 Td (  6. Meeting lasts 15-30 minutes max) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.0 Td (  7. End with something fun \(game, treat, activity\)) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
