BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (DISCUSSION CARDS \(Cut Out & Use\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Pull one card each meeting for bonus discussion:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (   1. What's one rule that needs changing? Why?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (   2. What's the best thing about our family?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (   3. Is anyone feeling overwhelmed this week?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.0 Td (   4. What chore system is working/not working?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.0 Td (   5. What should we do for fun this weekend?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.0 Td (   6. Is anyone having trouble with a friend?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.0 Td (   7. What meal should we cook together this week?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 578.0 Td (   8. What's something we could do for our community?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 564.0 Td (   9. Is screen time working fairly for everyone?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 550.0 Td (  10. What are we looking forward to this month?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 536.0 Td (  11. Does anyone need help with something?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 522.0 Td (  12. How can we be kinder to each other this week?) Tj ET
