BT /F2 11 Tf 54 556.4 Td (Method 3: Trial Period) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td (We'll try [decision] for ___ week\(s\) and review at next meeting.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 512.6 Td (Method 4: Rotate Choice) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 496.6 Td (This week [name] chooses. Next week [name] chooses.) Tj ET
